parameters: 中を調べてみる\c[27]【Ｈイベント】\c[0]

Nobody's around. This looks safe. If there's treasure, I'll
help myself to it\I[15]
Startle! You scoundrel! Who are you!?

To sneak into our storehouse, you are a bold and audacious
thief! There's only one entrance! There's no escape?
Surrender quietly!
~~~~!? (Damn it! I let my guard down...!)

Hmm? By that attire, a woman...? Could it be, the infamous
Mouse Komachi--?

No, that's not it! It was by chance! I was just taking a
walk at night and happened to enter because the gate was
open by chance! I'm sorry!

Hmm... For someone who claims such, the treasure chest is
open, isn't it? You're the one who stole from it, right?

Uhh... I'm sorry. It was me. It was just a moment of
temptation...

I see. You're quite understanding for a girl. You seem to be
a first-time offender. If you return the stolen money, I
might forgive you.

However, you must accept your punishment. Shall we have a
night together here? Mufufu\I[15]

That's right. I shall enjoy your body for a bit. Strip down
quietly. Otherwise, I'll hand you over to the magistrate. I
won't say it twice?

Yes... I understand... (I have no choice. I'll seduce him
and make my escape.)

--Karin stripped and surrendered her body to the night
patrol samurai.

Phew... My, what a fine body you have, girl. It's a pity for
just one night. Would you consider becoming my mistress?
What is your name?
--As the samurai spoke, Karin had already vanished.

What, she's already fled from the storehouse? The safe is
back to normal, well, all's well that ends well. Rather, I'm
fortunate to have had my way with a woman for free.
Muhuhuhu...\I[15]
And so the night's affair came to an end...

Haa... haa... To be found in a place with no escape, that
truly scared me.

Really, I've been clumsy. Maybe my thieving has been going
too well until now...

--Giving up on tonight's activities, Karin decided to return
home.

(...I have a bad feeling about this. I'm not here to steal
today, so I should just quietly go home.)
